<!-- ==================== CONVERSATION 1 ==================== -->
<!-- SCENARIO: Nighttime Stash Tip in Garbage                    -->
<!-- An experienced stalker offers stash coordinates near the    -->
<!-- Garbage, but warns of mutant activity. Player can push for  -->
