<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_precond">
    <text>req_time_night,req_rank:trainee</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_timeout">
    <text>120</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_timeout_msg">
    <text>Signal's fading. Forget it, I'll find someone else.</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_open">
    <text>$player_name, you awake? Found something interesting. I was poking around near %garbage_panda_st% earlier and spotted a stash someone tried to hide under debris. Problem is, there's fresh mutant tracks all around it. Dogs, maybe worse. I'm not equipped to deal with that right now. You want the coordinates? Could be worth your time.</text>
</string>

<!-- Turn 1 Choices -->
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_choice_1">
    <text>Yeah, send me the location. I'll check it out.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_choice_2">
    <text>What kind of stash are we talking about? Ammo? Meds? Artifacts?</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_choice_3">
    <text>Nothing's free in the Zone. What do you want for the info?</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_choice_4">
    <text>Not tonight. Too dark, too risky. Pass.</text>
</string>

<!-- Turn 1 Replies -->
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_reply_1">
    <text>Sending coordinates now. Watch yourself out there, the tracks looked fresh. Probably a pack of dogs using the area as a feeding ground. If you make it, whatever's in there is yours. I just want to know what was inside, curiosity and all that.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_reply_2">
    <text>Hard to say. Container was sealed tight, military-grade lock from what I could see through the debris. Could be anything. That's what makes it interesting, or dangerous. Someone went through real effort to hide it.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_reply_3">
    <text>Come on, I'm not running a business here. Fine, call it 1500 RU for the exact coordinates. Or you could owe me a favor. Your call, $player_name.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_reply_4">
    <text>Fair enough. Zone doesn't forgive mistakes in the dark. Stay safe out there.</text>
</string>

<!-- Turn 1 Outcomes -->
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_outcome_1">
    <text>watch_location_trigger:st_gar_smart_terrain_3_7_name:spawn_mutant:dog:15:85,reward_stash,reward_gw:5:stalker</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_outcome_2">
    <text>none</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_outcome_3">
    <text>none</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_outcome_4">
    <text>reward_gw:2:stalker</text>
</string>

<!-- Turn 1 Continuations -->
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_cont_1">
