    <text>req_time_day,req_rank:experienced</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_timeout">
    <text>90</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_timeout_msg">
    <text>*static* ...guess I'm on my own. Wouldn't be the first time.</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_open">
    <text>$player_name, I need help. Took a bad hit near %agroprom_panda_st%, bleeding pretty good. Got a bandage on it but I'm low on meds and there's movement in the treeline. Can't tell if it's stalkers or mutants. My PDA's showing you're the closest friendly. Can you do anything?</text>
</string>

<!-- Turn 1 Choices -->
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_choice_1">
    <text>Hold position, I'm coming to you. Sending you my approach vector now.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_choice_2">
    <text>How bad is the wound? Can you move at all?</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_choice_3">
    <text>I can dispatch a courier with meds. That's the best I can do from here.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_choice_4">
    <text>Sorry, I'm in a bad spot myself. Can't help right now.</text>
</string>

<!-- Turn 1 Replies -->
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_reply_1">
    <text>Thank god. I'll hold here and try to stay quiet. PDA marker is active, you should see my position. Hurry, $player_name, the movement in the trees is getting closer.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_reply_2">
    <text>Leg's torn up, hit something sharp going over a barricade. Can walk, but slow. If those are snorks in the trees I'm dead before I make fifty meters. I need options, not questions.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_reply_3">
    <text>A courier? That'll take time I might not have. But medkits and bandages would keep me going. If you can't come yourself, I'll take what I can get.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_reply_4">
    <text>Yeah... yeah, I get it. Zone doesn't wait for anyone. I'll try to crawl to cover. If I make it, I owe the Zone another day. If not... well. Good luck out there, $player_name.</text>
</string>

<!-- Turn 1 Outcomes -->
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_outcome_1">
    <text>watch_location:st_agr_smart_terrain_5_7_name:100,chance:50:spawn_mutant:snork:120,reward_gw:10:stalker,reward_rep:10</text>
</string>
