<!-- ===== TURN 2: Player asked about the wound ===== -->
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t2_choice_1">
    <text>Alright, I'm heading your way. Mark your position and stay low.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t2_choice_2">
    <text>Try to move toward the road. I'll send someone to meet you halfway.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t2_choice_3">
    <text>I'll call in a friendly patrol. They might reach you before I can.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t2_choice_4">
    <text>If you can walk, head north. There should be a camp up that way.</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t2_reply_1">
    <text>Position marked. I'm behind the concrete wall, east side. If something jumps me before you arrive, at least you'll know where to find what's left. Hurry.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t2_reply_2">
    <text>The road? That's open ground. But if someone's coming to meet me... alright, I'll try. Give me a few minutes to stabilize and start moving. Don't let me down.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t2_reply_3">
    <text>A patrol? That'd be a miracle right about now. If they show up, I'll make sure people know who sent them. You're a good one, $player_name.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t2_reply_4">
    <text>North... right, the old camp near the underground entrance. Long walk on a bad leg, but better than sitting here waiting to die. Thanks for the tip at least.</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t2_outcome_1">
    <text>watch_location:st_agr_smart_terrain_5_7_name:100,chance:50:spawn_mutant:snork:120,reward_gw:15:stalker,reward_rep:10</text>
