<!-- ===== TURN 3: NPC is attempting to move ===== -->
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t3_choice_1">
    <text>Good, keep moving. I see the patrol heading your direction.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t3_choice_2">
    <text>If you make it through this, come find me. I could use someone tough.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t3_choice_3">
    <text>Watch your six. If those were snorks, they'll chase movement.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t3_choice_4">
    <text>You've got this. Signal me when you're clear.</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t3_reply_1">
    <text>I see them! Two guys coming up the road. I think I'm going to make it. $player_name, I won't forget this. If you ever need backup, you know who to call.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t3_reply_2">
    <text>Recruit me? After seeing how you handle things over PDA, yeah, I'd follow you. Let me heal up first. Give me a day and I'll find you. Count on it.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t3_reply_3">
    <text>Noted. Moving low and quiet. I can hear something behind me but I'm not looking back. If this is it, at least someone tried to help. Thanks, stalker.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_2_t3_reply_4">
    <text>Almost to the road. Leg's screaming but the bleeding slowed. I'll ping you when I'm safe. Keep your PDA on. You earned a drink when we cross paths.</text>
</string>

